{"serial": "63030", "department_serial": 59, "code": "SS6037", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "The Principle of Radar Remote Sensing Ⅰ", "ch": "雷達遙測大氣原理 I"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "朱延祥與蘇清論老師共同授課"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chu, Yen-Hsyang", "Su, Ching-Lun"], "ch": ["朱延祥", "蘇清論"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S4", "room": "917"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "太空科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Space Science and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 20, "remark": {"ch": "朱延祥與蘇清論老師共同授課", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程核心內容在於介紹剖風儀理論與實務相關知識，透過背景大氣、折射指數與雷達系統的介紹與說明，詳細推導大氣雷達回波機制以及相關雷達測量大氣技術，使同學擁有完整的剖風儀理論知識與實務訊號分析能力。", "en": "“Through introducing background knowledge of atmospheric refractivity、radar system、EM wave scattering/reflection, the core objective of this course is to teach student specilized expertise of windprofiler and knowledge of practically analyzing  windprofiler echoes.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "前言(大氣折射指數之理論推導，大氣結構與運動，亂流概念，大氣目標物之分類，頻率選擇要素，雷達歷史概述); 雷達系統與噪音(雷達系統方塊圖，噪音分類，噪音指數，發射機，濾波器概念，匹配濾波器原理，濾波器設計，混波器，相位陣列天線理論，距離權重函數); 大氣雷達回波機制(亂流散設，佛氏反射，佛氏散射，流星尾回波機制)；大氣雷達技術(空間天線漂移法，都卜勒波束法，雷達干涉法，同相雷達影像法，距離影像法)；閃爍理論(Rytov近似，Born近似，前向散射理論)", "en": "“Introduction(atmospheric refractive index, atmospheric structure, turbulence concept, targets for the echoes of windprofiler, operational frequency determination, histry of atmospheric radar development); Radar system and noise(noise characteristics, noise figure, transmitter and receiver, matched filter, phase array antenna, range weighting function); Echoing mechanism of windprofiler(turbulence scatter, Fresnel reflection, Fresnel scatter, Rayleight scatter, meteor trail scatter/reflection); Atmospheric radar techniques(spaced antenna drift, Doppler beam swing, radar interferometer, coherent radar imaging, range imaging); Scintillation theory(Rytov and Born approximations, forward scatter theort)“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“Tartarskii, V.I., Wave propagation in random atmosphere, 1961\nA large number of related papers published in academic journals, such as JGR, Radio Science, JAS, JASTP, JATP, and so on.“", "en": "“Tartarskii, V.I., Wave propagation in random atmosphere, 1961\nA large number of related papers published in academic journals, such as JGR, Radio Science, JAS, JASTP, JATP, and so on.“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n實習/實驗\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "Practical Training Lab", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "40％-考試\n30％-報告與作業\n20％-討論與出席／課堂表現\n10％-實作與實驗", "en": "40％-exam\n30％-presentation and assignment\n20％-discussion and attendance performace\n10％-practice and experiment"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三(07:30-10:00pm)，星期四(07:30-10:00pm)，星期五(02-05pm)", "en": "\"Wednesday(07:30-10:00pm), Thursday (07:30-10:00pm"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n雷達與電磁波觀測", "en": "高層大氣科學與電離層物理\n\n\n、\n\n\n雷達與電磁波觀測"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "太空科學知識的建立", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "日地系統觀測技術的培養", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "整合創新與獨立思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資料分析能力的養成", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "數值模式的建立與應用", "rating": "(0)無", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "研究結果的表達及呈現", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "跨領域與團隊合作的能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Buildup of Space science know